<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的！？<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然丟下我一個人在這裡等了你<tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x2" />年，<delay20 />
你之前都去哪裡了？<delay8 />在做什麼事呀？<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不是啦，<delay8 />其實我也不是在怪你<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
總之，能再見到你真是太好了。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歡迎你回來！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay20 />
