<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這座島也變得沒什麼生氣<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呀，<delay8 />很討厭陰沉的氣氛，<delay20 />
如果你不在這裡，<delay8 />我也會覺得很苦惱的。<10_4 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你願意回來這裡喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你好嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺已經好一陣子，<delay8 />
