我都快想不起以前和你說過什麼話了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且差一點就要把你<delay8 />
也一起忘了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啦，剛才都是說笑的～<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歡迎你回來，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />初次見面<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的！<delay8 />你之前都跑到哪裡去了呀？<delay20 />
這麼長的時間裡都放著這座島不管……<delay8 />
真是太過分了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家都因為見不到你，<delay8 />
覺得很寂寞耶！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！？<10_4 />
