肯定有很多想做的事吧？<pageBreak />現在就在<tag a="110" b="33" />上，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />盡情去做你想做的事吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不會吧！？<delay8 />你是<tag a="110" b="4" />嗎！？<10_4 />
