連我最喜歡的<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />都變得很無趣，<delay8 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算吃<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />也覺得食之無味呢。<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之，我想說的是……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實人家真的好寂寞啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀呀，<delay8 />真是好久不見了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />居然讓我一個人在島上等你這麼久，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你到底<delay8 />去做什麼了呀？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過看到你這麼有精神，真是太好了。<delay20 />
我想不管在什麼地方，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你肯定都很忙吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天在島上就讓自己好好放鬆，
慢慢來吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
